window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The marauders, vicious alien predators, brought us to our knees. </p><p>They destroyed our fleets. They burned our cities. They butchered millions. </p><p>But now we fight back. </p><p>Across the ruins of Earth, we rise in rebellion. In the depths of space, we seek allies. And our last warship prepares for one final battle. </p><p>It's a time for heroes. A time to show our human pride. Because Earth is our home. Earth is our birthright. Earth is eternal. </p><p>We will save it. Or we will die on our feet. </p>"; 
